PM UTC (10:00 PM Monday April 13), so this briefing covers the day and sets up for Tuesday.\n\n\nNow I'll format this as a status report."},{"type":"text","text":"🌅 **ORBIS MORNING BRIEFING**\n📅 Monday, April 13, 2026\n⏰ 10:00 PM UTC | 5:00 AM UTC+7\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n**1️⃣ YESTERDAY'S COMPLETED TASKS**\n\n✅ **AHV Works Review** — FULL REVIEW COMPLETE (commit 84cdb2d)\n✅ **Session Recovery** — Crash at 00:34 UTC (HTTP 500 / context overflow), fully recovered on model `AHV-Holding-DEV`\n✅ **FE Sync** — Frontend fully synchronized with remote develop ✅\n✅ **DTLX/QLHV Systems** — Stable, shared DB architecture operational\n✅ **34-Agent Ecosystem** — SKILL_GATES, HANDOVER/FEEDBACK, OPENSPEC all verified ✅\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n**2️⃣ TODAY'S PRIORITIES**\n\n🔴 **P0 — AHV Works Fixes** — 13 unresolved P0 issues queued for resolution\n🟡 **Stitch MCP Wrapper** — Complete integration testing post-gateway restart\n🟡 **stitch-connect Skill** — Update to use MCP wrapper (replacing OAuth flow)\n🔵 **BE Notification System** — Local behind remote by 11 commits; notification system feature pending merge\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n**3️⃣ BLOCKERS & RISKS**\n\n⚠️ **BE Merge Conflict** — Backend is 11 commits behind remote on `notification-system`; remote is 2 commits ahead on `data-isolation`. **Lead decision required** before merge can proceed.\n\n⚠️ **Context Overflow Risk** — Session crash root cause identified (200k+ tokens / model instability). Monitor session health closely.\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n**Pipeline Status:** 🟢 HEALTHY\n**Active Agents:** 34 (v4 ecosystem)\n**Active Session:** telegram:group:-5212380728\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\nOrbis 🌐 — Global Orchestrator"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":328,"output":570,"totalTokens":17958,"cacheRead":14121,"cacheWrite":2939,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776117671474,"responseId":"062c9aa87844c59bbd285766e62b966f","__openclaw":